title: WSB's Weekend Bite: The Market Bottoms Likely Next Year With Katie Stockton
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description:
This week we're joined by Katie Stockton, Founder and Managing Partnerat Fairlead Strategies, to dive into what the market technicals are telling her about where the US markets head from here. We also explore the Fairlead Tactical Sector ETF (TACK) and Kim Khan covers next week's potential market-moving events in this week's Catalyst Watch.
